The '''Bare Forest''' was a [[Mountain/Legends|mountain]] valley located on [[Zelos II]]. A rocky valley studded with cusps of [[Conifer/Legends|conifer]] [[Tree/Legends|trees]], it was located in the northern part of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] main continent at some 1,200 [[Meter/Legends|meters]] above sea level. It was home to a tiny [[Worm/Legends|worm]]-like creature whose enzymes could sometimes [[Zombie/Legends|animate]] corpses, hence it was often called the '''Forest of the Walking Dead'''.

